Restore a Previous Version of a Dataflow

In CRM Analytics, click Data Manager in the left pane. Click the Dataflows & Recipes tab. Open a dataflow, then click the history icon. All versions of the dataflow appear in the Versions panel.

Revert to a previous version by clicking its name and then Update Dataflow. To delete a previous version, click the dropdown and click Delete.

For details, see Backup and Restore Previous Versions of Analytics Assets with History API.
